Package frc.utils

Class DriveSignal

  • java.lang.Object
    • frc.utils.DriveSignal
  • public class DriveSignal
extends java.lang.Object
    Small data structure to simplify the issuing of demands to the drivebase by encapsulating the left and right powers as well as whether or not the brakes should be enabled on the drivebase motors or not.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field Description
      static DriveSignal BRAKE
      Issues a demand of zero to the motors and enables the brakes.
      static DriveSignal NEUTRAL
      Issues a demand of zero to the motors and disables the brakes.
